{"tid":2306428,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"永安旅遊裁員約120人　約佔編制兩成","createTime":"2020-11-30T12:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T12:26:49.000Z","uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3bdce0afc28971f7956220f1cc393fd64daf3c3f","tid":2306428,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:07:36.000Z","msg":"永安旅遊裁員約120人 約佔編制兩成<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562828-20201130.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562828-20201130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xBhXM9JohKQ1t0lxADMilzY%3D&h=890a982d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562828-20201130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b31d6a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562828-20201130.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a805a876039a4c0b09a4a6ebb48c7f800cf76700","tid":2306428,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:07:55.000Z","msg":"永安旅遊宣布削減約120名員工，人數約佔整體員工編制兩成。<br />\n<br />\n永安表示，在現時疫情下，本港及外地的出入境防疫政策仍未見放寬，令旅遊業務恢復無期，根據國際航運機構的預測，未來一至兩年亦難以回復過往的出行規模。<br />\n<br />\n現時的人員數目遠超於未來的業務需求，隨著保就業計劃結束，人力成本將帶來難以負荷的壓力，因此在迫不得已的情況下，進行適當的架構精簡和業務重組。<br />\n<br />\n受措施影響的涉及約120名員工，分佈於不同部門，公司將以一個月代通知金，按僱傭條例計算相關離職補償。至於仍然留任的員工，則需繼續放取若干天數的無薪假。"},{"pid":"2a951c82857767df0d9567516695888f4d57fd1c","tid":2306428,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca31f428d3a5cf67d18870da43132f346d056c7a","tid":2306428,"uid":256215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"有唔少行業根本唔使保就業津貼。例如住宅管理根本唔會受影響，但收到D津貼好多都唔補比業主，自己生吞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8641e32a3add2154b92f1714eb6817d61a72